This house was built in 2020. Great wide entrance to the home. Bedrooms and closets with carpets were changed to laminate vinyl flooring. There have been Cabinets installed in the laundry room and the Garage. This Beautiful Ventana Community in Riverview presents Amenities like Community Pool, Clubhouse, Playground, Pickle Ball Courts and more. Located close to Great Highly Rated Schools,entertainment, dining, shopping areas, close to I75, Veterans Crosstown, Tampa International Airport, MacDill AFB, Sporting Events, Beaches Throughout Tampa Bay......
